    6 │ 
  
  i every() returns true and some() returns false for an empty array, so the check does not change the result. Remove it.
  
  i This rule belongs to the nursery group, which means it is not yet stable and may change in the future. Visit https://biomejs.dev/linter/#nursery for more information.
  
  i Unsafe fix: Remove the redundant length check.
  
    4 │ const·a·=·array.length·===·0·||·array.every(Boolean);
      │           ----------------------                     

